Cam::

She was now 700 yards from the base and getting lost. She looked 
around the trees and didn't see anything that looked familiar to her. 
She started running along the stream, but it was still the other way. 
She looked up at a bird when she felt the ground give way under her. 
She fell down the embankment of a river. She she hit her head on a 
large rock and landed in the water. The fast pace of the river 
carried her far down stream, down towards Hydras base.Her little fox 
body washed up on the shore of the river near the base. Her little 
maximal signature would have been picked up soon.
